History: this code was extracted from the `archimedes.tree` package (where the
Pine Tree Labs portion was previously distributed under GPL-3.0-or-later) and
relicensed by the copyright holder to MIT for standalone reuse. The tree
topology, @struct/field, the node registry, ravel, and the pydantic-backed
config layer (StructConfig/UnionConfig) are all carried over. The only upstream
coupling deliberately dropped is the *casadi* dependency: ravel is reimplemented
to be coercion-free, so it preserves symbolic array leaves via numpy dispatch
(__array_function__) and the .dtype/.astype duck-typed surface without importing
casadi.
